    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This demo is a 2h long experience that gives you a taste of the game's first areas, friends, foes and gameplay systems.<br><br>《古骸低语》是一款地牢探索游戏，每个转角背后，都藏有新发现。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一个深邃的、手工打造的世界，触手可及，沉浸感十足。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一路上，你将面对恐怖怪物，挑战令人敬畏的强敌，并邂逅稀奇古怪的人物！</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/fe8f1fa11d5d991ba730eed66f3a9fba.poster.avif?t=1771410919\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/fe8f1fa11d5d991ba730eed66f3a9fba.webm?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/fe8f1fa11d5d991ba730eed66f3a9fba.mp4?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/33e15cb23cd8b439dcb515b70de96eb3.poster.avif?t=1771410919\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/33e15cb23cd8b439dcb515b70de96eb3.webm?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br>精妙而曲折的关卡设计</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坠入地底深渊，探索无数无缝衔接的交错区域，揭开其中隐藏的秘密，尽情迷失其间吧。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/fe8f1fa11d5d991ba730eed66f3a9fba.poster.avif?t=1771410919\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/fe8f1fa11d5d991ba730eed66f3a9fba.webm?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/fe8f1fa11d5d991ba730eed66f3a9fba.mp4?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>海量独特装备等你收集</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用长剑、长鞭、手枪、重炮、圣物，施展魔法从敌阵中杀出一条血路。每一件装备都拥有其独特的用途。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/65a837ca3e3e2ba6b0a94805cce915af.poster.avif?t=1771410919\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/65a837ca3e3e2ba6b0a94805cce915af.webm?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/65a837ca3e3e2ba6b0a94805cce915af.mp4?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>清爽的复古现代画风</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《古骸低语》这个引人入胜的世界里，目之所及皆采用深受喜爱的复古现代低多边形风格渲染（支持特效自定义！）。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/0eac4c95f5849dce772531e76fc68ab2.poster.avif?t=1771410919\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/0eac4c95f5849dce772531e76fc68ab2.webm?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/0eac4c95f5849dce772531e76fc68ab2.mp4?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/5689d82deafbdb5f091923e46d948163.poster.avif?t=1771410919\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/5689d82deafbdb5f091923e46d948163.webm?t=1771410919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br>聆听骸骨的召唤吧!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一座潮湿、阴暗的维多利亚风格城市，匍匐在无星之夜下。它的市民们为欲望所驱，疯狂地刨掘着土地，渴望挖出零星的琥珀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城市之下，埋藏着不为人知的疆域。黑暗之中，充斥着难以想象的恐怖与光怪陆离的生物。而在那深渊至深处，一丝微光正引人侧目……<br><br>聆听骸骨的召唤吧!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132850/extras/5bb7f3116e8534f671d7be6941cb4678.avif?t=1771410919\" width=606 height=572 /></span></p>",
